missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-01.md:36:- or fatal because it depends on arbitrary representation gerrymandering.
missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-01.md:68:The attacker is also right that the chain needs a constructive revision loop instead of only one-way elimination, and that failure of representation robustness should not automatically count as failure of theorem usefulness.
