./missions/navier-stokes/steps/step-001/explorations/exploration-003/REPORT.md:162:- **P_k^1 is harmonic:** −ΔP_k^1 = 0 in [T_{k−1},1]×B_{k−2/3}. This is the "non-local" part carrying global pressure information. It is controlled by Lemma 7 using the *global* ||P||_{L^p(L¹)} norm:
