missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:59:- Spectators are being treated too late. If they matter enough to kill the window, they matter enough to belong in the exact support audit from Step 1 onward. Deferring them to Step 4 makes the earlier subsystem look cleaner than it really is.
missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:60:- "Measure how long the phase-locking manifold or near-manifold persists" sounds numerical and trajectory-specific. That is weak evidence unless the chain states a robustness standard: open set of initial data, codimension-one tuning, or exact invariant family.
