missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:70:- The handoff menu is too coarse. "Coefficient rigidity" or "no honest delayed window" is not yet reusable unless the chain has proved that the obstruction survives changes of support size, geometry class, or role assignment.
